            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%B9%BF%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E12%E4%BE%8B%E7%B4%AF%E8%AE%A1139%E4%BE%8B%23&amp;from=default">#广西新增12例累计139例#</a>】2月3日0-24时，广西壮族自治区共新增新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎确诊病例12例，其中南宁5例、柳州1例、北海1例、防城港2例、钦州1例、河池2例。<br>目前全区累计报告确诊病例139例，累计出院病例7例。现有重症病例8例（南宁1例、桂林1例、防城港5例、河池1例） ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IsB3DaBpO" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4468156372527108:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4468156372527108&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

        <div class="media_box">

                            <!--图片个数大于1，不渲染卡片-->

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【四川雅安一69岁<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E9%9A%90%E7%9E%92%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E8%87%B430%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E6%8A%A4%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%A6%23&amp;from=default">#男子隐瞒行程致30多名医护人员密切接触#</a>】2月3日晚间，四川雅安市应对新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情应急指挥部办公室发布通告称，一69岁确诊患者治疗中多次隐瞒自己途径武汉汉口返回雅安事实，致治疗中30多名医护密切接触。通告如下：<br>　　侯某，男，现年69岁，天全县 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IsxDV6Il9" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4468025111600415:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4468025111600415&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【这场战“疫”怎么打？习近平这么说！】①尽快找差距、补短板，同时间赛跑、与病魔较量；②疫情防控坚持全国一盘棋；③坚决反对形式主义、官僚主义；④努力提高收治率和治愈率、降低感染率和病死率；⑤要加大科研攻关力度；⑥依法打击各类违法犯罪…<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a> 这次大考，我们有信心一定过！ ​​​​                                            </div>

                    <!-- 回复 -->

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a> 【专家：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%8A%B6%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23&amp;from=default">#没有发现宠物传染新型冠状病毒#</a>】北京地坛医院感染二科主任医师蒋荣猛表示：感染人的病毒并不意味着能感染其他动物。目前为止没有发现宠物感染冠状病毒传播给人，也没有发现病人传染给猫和狗发病的情况。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=人民日报">@人民日报</a> <a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4468009559176892:1042163-video:1042163%3A4468006042927123:page_100206_home:2286908003:4468009559176892:2286908003" title="人民日报的微博视频" href="http://t.cn/A6PTIA47" alt="http://t.cn/A6PTIA47" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>人民日报的微博视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

        <div class="WB_detail">
                            <div class="WB_info">
                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【专家说明病毒空气中存活时间<img class="W_img_face" render="ext" src="//img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/48/2018new_huatong_org.png" title="[话筒]" alt="[话筒]" type="face" style="visibility: hidden;">】专家表示，病毒从人体出来后很快沉降，不会在空气中漂浮。从这个意义讲，<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23&amp;from=default">#空气中不会有病毒#</a>。但飞沫可以沉降，病毒可以落在物体表面，人可以通过手来接触到病毒。病毒在光滑的物体表面可以存活数小时，温度湿度合适的环境能存活一天，有发现可 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IswZovkWz" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467999987468679:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467999987468679&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
